ser, ir, and ver. They conjugate as follows and the best advice is memorization.<br />SER: Era, eras, era, \u00E9ramos, \u00E9rais, eran<br />IR: Iba, ibas, iba, \u00EDbamos, \u00EDbais, iban <br />Ver: Ve\u00EDa, ve\u00EDas, ve\u00EDa, ve\u00EDamos, ve\u00EDais, ve\u00EDan<br /></font></td></tr></table></center></body></html>';


